name: Bright Flowers Wine Glass
description:
Hand painted 12 oz wine glass. Hand wash only. Each glass is unique. Each glass sold separately.

Featuring a bright purple, pink, blue, or white flower design, this glass makes a great gift for birthdays, Mother's Day, or just to celebrate Spring!

Glasses are custom made as ordered. Other colors or additional design may be requested. If customization is desired please send requests to me in the note to seller section during check out.
